  <brief_title>Needs in Education for Pulmonary or Cardiopulmonary Transplanted Cystic Fibrosis Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessing of the Educational Needs of Patients Who Received a Lung Transplantation or a Simultaneous Heart-lung Transplantation for Mucoviscidosis</official_title>
